[Neurological signs are relatively non-specific, as a number of pesticides,
as well as botulism, may cause these clinical signs. - Mod.TG]
[Rapid tests for botulism, taking less than one hour, are widely available --
I have them in my lab. So I wonder why diagnosis is taking so long. - Mod.JW]
